data.name: Label2.Text
data.value:
Today you are going to embark on a challenging set of missions, in which you will be guesssing the correct words which co respond to the topic dispayed on the screen. There will be 5 missions, which will increase in difficulty each time
You will be required to guess a word relating to white collar. To do so, use the keyboard provided on the screen to guess a letter or type it in yourself.
You can play in two modes: Arcade and Campaign. In campaign you follow an intricate story line and guess all kinds of words, proggressing in dificulty each level. In arcade, it is a race against the clock to guess the names of the characters which pop up.
